data.description: Presenting an exquisite 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence in the coveted Asbel Estates! This 2009 MI Homes built masterpiece spans 3,390 sqft of luxurious living space, offering a perfect blend of elegance and functionality. Upon entering, be greeted by the charm of a fenced-in backyard with vinyl, providing privacy and a secure space for outdoor activities. The first floor unveils an in-law suite, ensuring versatile living arrangements for your family's unique needs. Enjoy the convenience of a water softener and revel in the tranquility of the rear lanai, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Entertain effortlessly with a layout that includes a separate family room, a spacious living room, and a formal dining room. The kitchen is complete with granite countertops, stainless-steel appliances, and a charming breakfast nook overlooking the rear lanai. Upstairs, discover a sprawling 27x15 private master bedroom with a sitting area, an office space, and an expansive walk-in closet. The master bath is a luxurious retreat, boasting an enclosed water closet, dual vanities, a full shower, and a rejuvenating soaking tub. All additional bedrooms are generously sized, offering ample closet space for storage. Whether hosting guests or enjoying family time, this home caters to both style and practicality. Beyond the property, Asbel Estates enhances your lifestyle with its desirable amenities, including a dog park, playground, basketball courts, and volleyball—creating a community that goes beyond the boundaries of your home. Seize this opportunity to own a residence in the sought-after Asbel Estates. Schedule your viewing today!
